name: iata-icao-airports-list
description: This list contains the airport codes of [IATA airport code](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Air_Transport_Association_airport_code) and [ICAO airport code](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Civil_Aviation_Organization_airport_code) grouped based on the country code (ISO3166-1) and region name (ISO3166-2) supported in IP2Location geolocation database.
